summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing a pedestrian walkway easement agreement across certain City property (Lighting Department electric transmission line right-of-way) in the Northwest quarter of the Northwest quarter and the Southwest quarter of the Township 28 North, Range 5 East, W.M. in Snohomish County, Washington, and accepting an easement across a certain property in the Northwest quarter of Section 34, Township 28 North, Range 5 East, W.M. as consideration therefor.
